3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 0-8.962L8.5 1.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937.5l1.582-6.135a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 8.962 0L22.063.5a2 2 0 0 0 1.437 1.437l6.135 1.581a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 0 8.962l-6.135 1.582a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-8.962 0z\"></path></svg> Introducing v2.0 AI Voice Agents</span><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl\">Never miss a lead. <br class=\"hidden sm:block\"/><span class=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-blue-500\">Automate your callbacks.</span></h1><p class=\"mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-muted-foreground md:text-xl leading-relaxed\">CallbackOS instantly dials back missed calls, speaks naturally to your customers, answers FAQs, and books appointments while you sleep.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center pt-4\"><a href=\"/signup\"><button data-slot=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 rounded-md has-[&gt;svg]:px-4 h-12 px-8 text-base group\">Start Your Free Trial<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right ml-2 h-4 w-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button></a><a href=\"#demo\"><button data-slot=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive border shadow-xs hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground dark:bg-input/30 dark:border-input dark:hover:bg-input/50 rounded-md has-[&gt;svg]:px-4 h-12 px-8 text-base bg-background/50 backdrop-blur-sm\">Listen to a Demo</button></a></div><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground font-medium pt-2\">No credit card required · 14-day free trial</p></div></section><section class=\"w-full py-12 border-y border-border/50 bg-secondary/30\"><div class=\"container px-4 md:px-6 text-center\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider mb-8\">Trusted by 1000+ local businesses</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8 md:gap-16 opacity-50 grayscale\"><div class=\"font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl font-mono tracking-tighter text-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-foreground/20\"></div> <!-- -->Acme Corp</div><div class=\"font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl font-mono tracking-tighter text-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-foreground/20\"></div> <!-- -->GlobalTech</div><div class=\"font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl font-mono tracking-tighter text-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-foreground/20\"></div> <!-- -->Local Dental</div><div class=\"font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl font-mono tracking-tighter text-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-foreground/20\"></div> <!-- -->AutoFix</div><div class=\"font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl font-mono tracking-tighter text-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-foreground/20\"></div> <!-- -->Prime Plumbers</div><div class=\"font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl font-mono tracking-tighter text-foreground/80 flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-md bg-foreground/20\"></div> <!-- -->Elite Legal</div></div></div></section><section id=\"how-it-works\" class=\"w-full py-20 md:py-32\"><div class=\"container px-4 md:px-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\">How CallbackOS Works</h2><p class=\"max-w-[700px] text-muted-foreground md:text-lg\">Set up your AI agent in minutes. Our system handles the rest securely and automatically.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><div class=\"h-12 w-12 rounded-xl border border-border bg-secondary/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary\">1</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Connect Your Phone</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground\">Link your existing business number via Twilio or direct SIP trunk. No need to change your provider.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><div class=\"h-12 w-12 rounded-xl border border-border bg-secondary/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary\">2</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Train the AI</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground\">Upload your PDFs, price lists, and FAQs. The agent learns your business instantly and follows your exact scripts.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all\"><div class=\"h-12 w-12 rounded-xl border border-border bg-secondary/50 flex items-center justify-center mb-6\"><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary\">3</span></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold mb-2\">Auto-Dial Back</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground\">When you miss a call, the AI calls them back immediately, answers questions, and logs the transcript directly in your dashboard.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"features\" class=\"w-full py-20 md:py-32 bg-secondary/20 border-y border-border/50\"><div class=\"container px-4 md:px-6\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\">Built for Scale</h2><p class=\"max-w-[700px] text-muted-foreground md:text-lg\">Everything you need to run a 24/7 reception desk without hiring extra staff.</p></div><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-bot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 8V4H8\"></path><rect width=\"16\" height=\"12\" x=\"4\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M2 14h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 14h2\"></path><path d=\"M15 13v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 13v2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Human-like Voice</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Sub-500ms latency with ElevenLabs voice cloning for completely natural, interruption-aware conversations.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Knowledge Base</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Upload PDFs, websites, and text. The agent rigidly follows instructions and never hallucinates answers.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Smart Scheduling</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Configure exact operating hours, weekend logic, and specific time delays before the agent calls back.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-primary/10 text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-semibold\">Instant Escalation</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">If a caller is frustrated or asks for a human, the agent instantly pauses and SMS texts your manager.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"w-full py-20 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/5\"></div><div class=\"container px-4 md:px-6 relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl\">Stop leaving money on the table.</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground md:text-xl\">Every missed call is a missed customer. Install CallbackOS today and guarantee every lead is captured.</p><div class=\"pt-4\"><a href=\"/signup\"><button data-slot=\"button\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap font-medium transition-all disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg:not([class*=&#x27;size-&#x27;])]:size-4 shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 outline-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 rounded-md has-[&gt;svg]:px-4 h-14 px-10 text-lg w-full sm:w-auto shadow-lg shadow-primary/20\">Create Your Free Account</button></a></div><p class=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground pt-4\">Takes 2 minutes to set up. Cancel anytime.</p></div></section></main><footer class=\"w-full border-t border-border bg-background py-8 md:py-12\"><div class=\"container px-4 md:px-6 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-6 md:flex-row text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stro